    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Will we update via a direct link to a `.oramod` that is saved and unpacked into the support directory (or possibly kept packed and loaded from zip)?\n\nAs an extension idea related to bullet point 3 I'd like to see a place in the UI and in the mod directory for a changelog file that mod authors can include (not necessary!) that players can read and make the decision to upgrade or not based on the information provided.\n"
