    "body": "The current best practice for vanilla Tiberian Sun mods is to have a spawner which checks for updates and has a button to automatically download and install those. We were asked if such a content delivery feature (like we do for maps) is planned for OpenRA as well. http://www.ppmforums.com/viewtopic.php?p=533798#533798 You might want to take that into consideration.\n"
